ygData.messageBody:
Very nice to meet you also. It sounds like you're
doing a great job for being so new to the game. :)
Asking questions actually helps everyone too. Anytime
I can help you, just ask. I've toyed with starting
toons on other servers just for fun, so if I do, I'll
make sure to look you up. :)

Happy Hunting,
Ainthara
